  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK642">
<l>ākkamuṅ kēṭu mataṉāl varutalāṟ </l>
<l>kāttōmpal colliṉkaṭ cōrvu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Since (both) wealth and evil result from (their) speech, ministers should most carefully guard themselves against faultiness therein.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
